，同时，
\begin_inset Formula $M_{B}^{2}$
\end_inset

 前的系数是
\begin_inset Formula $y$
\end_inset

。例如
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\int\dif^{4}k\frac{\delta\left(y-\frac{k^{+}}{p^{+}}\right)}{D_{\phi}\left(k\right)^{a}D_{B}\left(p-k\right)^{2}D_{\Lambda}^{b}\left(k\right)}=\int\dif k_{\perp}^{2}\frac{y}{\overline{y}}\frac{\left(-\pi i\right)}{\overline{y}}\left(\frac{a}{D_{\phi B}^{a+1}D_{\Lambda B}^{b}}+\frac{b}{D_{\phi B}^{a}D_{\Lambda B}^{b+1}}\right)
\]

\end_inset

